{
  "texts": [
    "If students treat AI as a black box solution rather than a creativity aid, it could undermine learning goals.",
    "Students need support developing digital literacy to evaluate strengths, weaknesses, and appropriate applications.",
    "Poorly implemented AI also threatens student agency and diversity.",
    "Biased algorithms or limited training data can propagate harm (Zhai, 2022).",
    "Overreliance on standardized systems can ignore individual needs."
  ]
}